Larry WELENC, ON BEHALF OF Angeline T. WELENC (deceased), Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
STATE-WIDE INSURANCE CO., Defendant. M-1 September Term 2018
080446 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the motion for removal and other relief is denied.
